      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely<strong> </strong>dice the<strong> shallot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Peel and grate the<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Chop the<strong> chicken breasts</strong> into large, bite-sized pieces</p>",
